      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HAYOAK (7) went to the front in the early stages and kept going to record a commanding 12 metres win last start over 2230m at Globe Derby Park, following on from a strong second the run prior at Globe Derby Park. Should enjoy a nice smother from this draw and will be looking for a split at some stage. Taking on a better field but she is up to the task. CADENCE LANE (6) won at Globe Derby Park two runs ago but couldn't repeat the dose at her latest appearance over 2230m at Globe Derby Park, beaten 5 metres. Stepping up a level this time but on her best form she is good enough to take this out. TRANQUIL BILL (1) broke last start but still managed to fill a minor placing over 2230m at Globe Derby Park, finishing 14 metres from the winner.  Will enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position and another big run is likely. JANES GEM (2) must be respected after scoring last start by 2 metres at Globe Derby Park over 2230m.",
